    "Description": "We're looking for someone discreet to move a new batch of altruciatoxin to a number of buyers . Yeah, it's illegal, but only if you get caught. \n\nThe shipment is at <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4>. You'll need to take it to these drop points:\n\nDROP OFF LOCATIONS (ANY ORDER)\n\n~mission(SingleToMultiToken)\n\nBe sure your ship can carry size <EM4>~mission(MissionMaxSCUSize)</EM4> containers, and don't forget to pack a <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4>. Not sure how you're planning on moving the boxes, otherwise.\n\n-Twitch",
